<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Ok, well this weapon has become considerably harder to get.  Thining about going and ganking some spectres for this weapon? Forget it.  Now what you must do it go to Erudin,  (now this is very vague) talk to some guy.  He will tell you that there are these 3 guys planning on building a bridge and that you must go and take them out.  They are all around level 35, and are surrounded by level 30+ npc's.  You first must FIND them, then the next part is kiling them.  Gaining the faction for the deepwaterknights is virtually impossible as well.  One of the guys is a gnome, the other is a human. Not sure on the last but they are tough and they got backup.    So get ready to gear up with a full group of level 30+ and GOOD LUCK</font></td></tr></table>
